Evonet EHV Switchgear Data Analysis

1 Asset Quantity

There are 680 records for EHV Switchgear in the source data. Ignoring NA or default values:

  • The average year of manufacture is 1995.

  • The average number of customers is 2618.

2 Population Summary

An entry is deemed as unpopulated if it is either NA or blank. The chart below shows the fields provided in each source data item and indicates how populated each field is:

2.1 Asset ID

Asset_Number is the unique identifier. There is a total of 680 rows in the switchgear source data. There are 680 unique values for Asset_Number.
